---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="授業内容・料金｜IB専門家庭教師IBT"
  description="IB専門家庭教師IBTの授業内容と料金。入会金0円・チケット制。全科目マンツーマン指導、オンライン＆対面対応。無料体験受付中。"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
      "itemListElement": [
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "ホーム", "item": "https://ib-tutors.net/" },
        { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "授業内容・料金", "item": "https://ib-tutors.net/lessons-pricing/" }
      ]
    })} />
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify([
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Course",
        "name": "IB DP 個別指導コース",
        "description": "IB DP全科目対応のマンツーマン個別指導。TOK・EE・IA対策も含む。",
        "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "IBT（IB Tutors）", "url": "https://ib-tutors.net"},
        "hasCourseInstance": {"@type": "CourseInstance", "courseMode": "online"}
      },
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Course",
        "name": "IB MYP 個別指導コース",
        "description": "IB MYP全科目対応のマンツーマン個別指導。",
        "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "IBT（IB Tutors）", "url": "https://ib-tutors.net"},
        "hasCourseInstance": {"@type": "CourseInstance", "courseMode": "online"}
      }
    ])} />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ibt-gradient-start via-ibt-gradient-mid to-ibt-gradient-end py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <nav class="text-white/85 text-sm mb-4">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">ホーム</a>
        <span class="mx-2">&gt;</span>
        <span class="text-white">授業内容・料金</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">授業内容・料金</h1>
      <p class="text-white/80 mt-3 text-lg">入会金0円・チケット制。気軽に始められるIB専門指導</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Points Banner -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Point 1 -->
        <div class="bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-ibt-red-light/50">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0 1 15.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 0 1 3 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 0 0-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 0 0 3 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5Zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ibt-red text-3xl font-bold mb-1">0円</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text font-bold">入会金</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mt-1">初期費用は一切かかりません</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Point 2 -->
        <div class="bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-ibt-red-light/50">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0 3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0 0 13.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0 1 13.803-3.7l3.181 3.182" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ibt-red text-3xl font-bold mb-1">チケット制</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text font-bold">授業料</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mt-1">月額制ではなく受講した分だけ</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Point 3 -->
        <div class="bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-ibt-red-light/50">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 11.25v8.25a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5 1.5H5.25a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-1.5-1.5v-8.25M12 4.875A2.625 2.625 0 1 0 9.375 7.5H12m0-2.625V7.5m0-2.625A2.625 2.625 0 1 1 14.625 7.5H12m0 0V21m-8.625-9.75h18c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125h-18c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ibt-red text-3xl font-bold mb-1">60分無料</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text font-bold">体験授業</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mt-1">まずはお試しで講師の質を実感</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 授業内容 -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-ibt-bg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <p class="text-ibt-red font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4">LESSONS</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold">授業内容</h2>
        <p class="text-ibt-text-light mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">IBプログラムのあらゆる科目・課題に対応します</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          { title: 'DP科目指導', desc: '全科目対応。HL/SLそれぞれの出題傾向を踏まえた指導', icon: 'M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5' },
          { title: 'TOK（知の理論）対策', desc: 'プレゼン・エッセイの構成や採点基準を踏まえた実践指導', icon: 'M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 0 0 1.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 0 1-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 0 1-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 0 1-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.823 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 1 0-7.517 0c.85.493 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18' },
          { title: 'EE（課題論文）サポート', desc: 'テーマ選定から執筆・推敲まで、4,000語論文を完成に導く', icon: 'M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z' },
          { title: 'IA（内部評価）対策', desc: '各科目のIA要件を理解し、高得点を狙える成果物を作成', icon: 'M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 3 19.875v-6.75ZM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V8.625ZM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V4.125Z' },
          { title: 'CAS活動アドバイス', desc: 'Creativity・Activity・Serviceの活動計画と振り返りをサポート', icon: 'M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z' },
          { title: 'MYP・PYP科目指導', desc: 'IBの基礎段階から丁寧にサポート。学習習慣の土台を構築', icon: 'M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 0 0 6 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 1 6 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 0 1 6-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0 0 18 18a8.967 8.967 0 0 0-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25' },
          { title: '大学受験対策（IB入試）', desc: 'IBスコアを活用した国内外大学入試の戦略と対策', icon: 'M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3H21m-3.75 3H21' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-ibt-border p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow flex gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={item.icon} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 授業スタイル -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <p class="text-ibt-red font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4">LESSON STYLE</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold">授業スタイル</h2>
        <p class="text-ibt-text-light mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">ライフスタイルに合わせて選べる受講方法</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Online -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m15.75 10.5 4.72-4.72a.75.75 0 0 1 1.28.53v11.38a.75.75 0 0 1-1.28.53l-4.72-4.72M4.5 18.75h9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25h-9A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">オンライン</h3>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">Zoom等を使用。<br />海外在住でも受講可能</p>
        </div>

        <!-- In-person -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">対面</h3>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">講師の所在地による。<br />ご相談ください</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Duration -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-ibt-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-ibt-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">1回50分</h3>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">集中力が続く最適な時間設定。<br />無料体験は60分です</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 料金表 -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-ibt-bg">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <p class="text-ibt-red font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4">PRICING</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold">料金</h2>
        <p class="text-ibt-text-light mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">シンプルで分かりやすい料金体系</p>
      </div>
      <!-- 料金テーブル -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- 基本情報 -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-ibt-border p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mb-1">入会金</p>
            <p class="text-ibt-red text-3xl font-bold">0<span class="text-base text-ibt-text-light ml-1">円</span></p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-ibt-border p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mb-1">教材費</p>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold">原則0円</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-ibt-text-light mt-1">特定教材が必要な場合は事前にご案内します</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-ibt-border p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mb-1">無料体験</p>
            <p class="text-ibt-red text-xl font-bold">60分 x 1回</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- プログラム別料金 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-ibt-border overflow-hidden">
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-ibt-border">
                  <th class="px-3 md:px-6 py-4 text-left font-bold">プログラム</th>
                  <th class="px-3 md:px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold">オンライン<br /><span class="text-xs font-normal text-ibt-text-light">50分/回</span></th>
                  <th class="px-3 md:px-6 py-4 text-center font-bold">対面<br /><span class="text-xs font-normal text-ibt-text-light">50分/回</span></th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b border-ibt-border">
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5">
                    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mr-2">PYP</span>
                    <span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs hidden sm:inline">初等教育</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5 text-center">
                    <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold">4,840</span><span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs ml-1">円/回</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5 text-center">
                    <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold">5,258</span><span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs ml-1">円/回</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-ibt-border">
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5">
                    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mr-2">MYP</span>
                    <span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs hidden sm:inline">中等教育</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5 text-center">
                    <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold">6,050</span><span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs ml-1">円/回</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5 text-center">
                    <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold">6,468</span><span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs ml-1">円/回</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5">
                    <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 text-xs font-bold rounded-full mr-2">DP</span>
                    <span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs hidden sm:inline">ディプロマ</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5 text-center">
                    <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold">7,260</span><span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs ml-1">円/回</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-3 md:px-6 py-5 text-center">
                    <span class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold">7,678</span><span class="text-ibt-text-light text-xs ml-1">円/回</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm text-center mt-4">
          ※ 料金は税込です。前払いチケット制・月謝や長期契約なし。まとめ買いパックあり（4回/8回/12回/16回）。チケット有効期限は購入から6ヶ月間です。
        </p>

        <!-- 料金表直後CTA -->
        <div class="mt-10 bg-ibt-red-50 border border-ibt-red-light/50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-ibt-text font-bold text-lg md:text-xl mb-2">まずは60分の無料体験から</p>
          <p class="text-ibt-text-light text-sm mb-6">入会金0円・チケット制だから、いつでも気軽にスタートできます。無理な勧誘は一切ありません。</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
            <a
              href="/contact/"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-ibt-gradient-start to-ibt-gradient-end text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all text-base"
            >
              60分無料体験に申し込む
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://line.me/R/ti/p/@974okamx"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#06C755] text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity text-base"
            >
